blender: blender (3D Content Creation Suite)
blender:
blender: Blender is an integrated suite of tools enabling the creation of a 
blender: broad range of 3D content with the singular benefits of cross-
blender: platform interoperability. It can be used to create 3D 
blender: visualizations, stills as well as broadcast and cinema quality 
blender: video. It features fully integrated creation suite, offering a broad
blender: range of essential tools  for the creation of 3D content, including 
blender: modeling, uv-mapping, texturing, particle and other simulation, 
blender: scripting, rendering, compositing,post-production, and game creation.
